---
source: crates/carta/tests/golden_e2e.rs
expression: output
---
A plain © sign decodes in running text.

Monospace `&` decodes, as do a <sub>©</sub> subscript, a <sup>®</sup>
superscript, and a <s>©</s> deletion.

A link label [\&copy;](start) keeps the entity literal, and so does a
\&copy; span and a verbatim block:

    &copy;
